4-14", "dateLabelColor": "#1f883d"}, "P28": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/fu-wen-ben-bian-ji-qi-yin-qi-de-ye-mian-yi-chang-bug.html", "labels": ["fastadmin", "debug"], "postTitle": "\u5bcc\u6587\u672c\u7f16\u8f91\u5668\u5f15\u8d77\u7684\u9875\u9762\u5f02\u5e38bug", "postUrl": "post/fu-wen-ben-bian-ji-qi-yin-qi-de-ye-mian-yi-chang-bug.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/junwindxqw/junwindxqw.github.io/issues/28", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 370, "description": "<img width='606' height='237' alt='Image' src='https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/67f67838-9da7-4893-b586-a3bbfe203990' />\n\n<img width='589' height='213' alt='Image' src='https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/8cada708-d433-4f6f-a782-c3a12855b476' />\n\n\n\u56e0\u4e3a\u8fd9\u4e2a >  \u7b26\u53f7\u7684\u539f\u56e0\uff0c\u53ef\u80fd\u4f1a\u5bfc\u81f4html\u9875\u9762\u5143\u7d20\u7ed3\u6784\u51fa\u73b0\u95ee\u9898\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1776160870, "style": "", "script": "<script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/backtop.js'></script><script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/articletoc.js'></script><script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/lightbox.js'></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://github.com/junwindxqw.png", "createdDate": "2026-04-14", "dateLabelColor": "#1f883d"}, "P29": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/wsl-ji-ben-shi-yong.html", "labels": ["wsl"], "postTitle": "wsl\u57fa\u672c\u4f7f\u7528", "postUrl": "post/wsl-ji-ben-shi-yong.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/junwindxqw/junwindxqw.github.io/issues/29", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 641, "description": "```powershell\n// \u5b89\u88c5wsl\nwsl --install  \uff08\u81ea\u52a8\u5f00\u542f\u529f\u80fd + \u5b89\u88c5\u9ed8\u8ba4 Ubuntu\uff09\n\n// \u5217\u51fa\u53ef\u5728\u7ebf\u5b89\u88c5\u7684 Linux \u53d1\u884c\u7248\nwsl --list --online    // \u7b80\u5199 wsl -l -o\n\n// \u5b89\u88c5\u67d0\u53f0 Linux\uff08\u4f8b\uff1aUbuntu-24.04\uff09\nwsl --install -d Ubuntu-24.04\n\n// \u5217\u51fa\u5df2\u5b89\u88c5\u7684\nwsl -l -v\n\n// \u542f\u52a8\u67d0\u53f0 Linux\uff08\u8fdb\u5165\u9ed8\u8ba4\u53d1\u884c\u7248\uff09\nwsl\n// \u542f\u52a8\u6307\u5b9a Linux\nwsl -d Ubuntu-24.04\n\n// \u505c\u6b62\u6240\u6709\u5df2\u8fd0\u884c\u7684Linux\nwsl --shutdown\n\n// \u505c\u6b62\u67d0\u53f0\u8fd0\u884c\u7684Linux\nwsl --terminate Ubuntu-24.04   // \u7b80\u5199  wsl -t Ubuntu-24.04\n\n// \u5907\u4efd\u67d0\u53f0 Linux\uff08\u5bfc\u51fa\u4e3a .tar \u6587\u4ef6\uff09\nwsl --export Ubuntu-24.04 D:\\backup\\ubuntu2404.tar\n\n// \u5378\u8f7d\u67d0\u53f0Linux\u53d1\u884c\u7248\uff08\u5378\u8f7d\u524d\u5148\u505c\u6b62\u8fd0\u884c\uff09\nwsl --unregister Ubuntu-24.04\n\n// \u5bfc\u5165\u5907\u4efd\u597d\u7684\u67d0\u53f0 Linux\uff08\u6062\u590d\u7cfb\u7edf\uff09\nwsl --import \u65b0\u540d\u79f0 \u5b89\u88c5\u8def\u5f84 \u5907\u4efd\u6587\u4ef6.tar  // \u793a\u4f8b\uff1a wsl --import Ubuntu24 D:\\WSL\\Ubuntu24 D:\\backup\\ubuntu2404.tar\n```\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1776221576, "style": "", "script": "<script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/backtop.js'></script><script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/articletoc.js'></script><script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/lightbox.js'></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://github.com/junwindxqw.png", "createdDate": "2026-04-15", "dateLabelColor": "#1f883d"}, "P30": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/ji-huo-jb-jia.html", "labels": ["jetbrains", "\u6fc0\u6d3b"], "postTitle": "\u6fc0\u6d3bjb\u5bb6", "postUrl": "post/ji-huo-jb-jia.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/junwindxqw/junwindxqw.github.io/issues/30", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 128, "description": "> \u58f0\u660e\uff1a\u4ec5\u9650\u6d4b\u8bd5\u4f7f\u7528\uff0c\u8bf7\u652f\u6301\u6b63\u7248\u8f6f\u4ef6\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1776222513, "style": "", "script": "<script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/backtop.js'></script><script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/articletoc.js'></script><script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/lightbox.js'></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://github.com/junwindxqw.png", "createdDate": "2026-04-15", "dateLabelColor": "#1f883d"}, "P31": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/shang-gui-gu-qian-duan-zi-yuan.html", "labels": ["\u8d44\u6e90"], "postTitle": "\u5c1agui\u8c37\u524d\u7aef\u8d44\u6e90", "postUrl": "post/shang-gui-gu-qian-duan-zi-yuan.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/junwindxqw/junwindxqw.github.io/issues/31", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 226, "description": "\u5c1a\u7845\u8c37\u524d\u7aef\u5168\u5957\u89c6\u9891\u6559\u7a0b\nB\u7ad9\u76f4\u8fbe\u514d\u8d39\u5728\u7ebf\u770b\uff1ahttps://space.bilibili.com/302417610/channel/seriesdetail?sid=457615\n\u514d\u8d39\u89c6\u9891\u53ca\u8d44\u6599\u4e0b\u8f7d\u5730\u5740\uff1ahttps://pan.baidu.com/s/1EMt3ylnwyOmRyr8ssoPOzQ?pwd=yyds \u63d0\u53d6\u7801: yyds\n\n\u5b66\u4e60\u8def\u7ebf\u53ca\u4e0b\u8f7d\u5bfc\u822a\uff1ahttp://www.atguigu.com/html5_video.shtml#html\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1776223848, "style": "", "script": "<script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/backtop.js'></script><script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/articletoc.js'></script><script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/lightbox.js'></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://github.com/junwindxqw.png", "createdDate": "2026-04-15", "dateLabelColor": "#1f883d"}, "P32": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/a-li-yun-oss-gua-zai-dao-fu-wu-qi.html", "labels": ["oss\u5bf9\u8c61\u5b58\u50a8"], "postTitle": "\u963f\u91cc\u4e91oss\u6302\u8f7d\u5230\u670d\u52a1\u5668", "postUrl": "post/a-li-yun-oss-gua-zai-dao-fu-wu-qi.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/junwindxqw/junwindxqw.github.io/issues/32", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 493, "description": "```\nossfs ttxres /opt/oss_upload \\\n  -o url=oss-cn-guangzhou-internal.aliyuncs.com \\\n  -o passwd_file=/etc/passwd-ossfs \\\n  -o allow_other \\\n  -o mp_umask=022 \\\n  -o umask=022\n```\n\n- ttxres  Bucket\u6876\n-  /opt/oss_upload  \u672c\u5730\u8981\u6302\u8f7d\u7684\u76ee\u5f55\n- oss-cn-guangzhou-internal.aliyuncs.com  OSS \u5185\u7f51\u8bbf\u95ee\u5730\u5740\uff08\u5e7f\u5dde\u533a\uff09\n- -o passwd_file=/etc/passwd-ossfs  \u4ece\u6307\u5b9a\u6587\u4ef6\u8bfb\u53d6\u5bc6\u94a5\uff08AccessKey\uff09\uff0c \u6587\u4ef6\u683c\u5f0f\uff1aBucketName:AccessKeyID:AccessKeySecret  \u4e0d\u914d\u5219\u81ea\u52a8\u67e5\u627e\n- -o allow_other   \u5141\u8bb8\u6240\u6709\u7cfb\u7edf\u7528\u6237\u8bbf\u95ee\u8fd9\u4e2a\u6302\u8f7d\u76ee\u5f55\n-  -o mp_umask=022 \u6302\u8f7d\u540e\u76ee\u5f55 / \u6587\u4ef6\u6743\u9650\n- -o umask=022 \u65b0\u521b\u5efa\u7684\u6587\u4ef6 / \u76ee\u5f55\u6743\u9650\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1776243880, "style": "", "script": "<script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/backtop.js'></script><script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/articletoc.js'></script><script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/lightbox.js'></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://github.com/junwindxqw.png", "createdDate": "2026-04-15", "dateLabelColor": "#1f883d"}, "P33": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/ubuntu-an-zhuang-docker.html", "labels": ["docker", "wsl"], "postTitle": "ubuntu\u5b89\u88c5docker", "postUrl": "post/ubuntu-an-zhuang-docker.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/junwindxqw/junwindxqw.github.io/issues/33", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 1702, "description": "1. \u5148\u68c0\u67e5systemd\u662f\u5426\u5f00\u542f\uff0c/etc/wsl.conf \u4e2d systemd=true \n```\nwsl --terminate Ubuntu   \u7ec8\u6b62\nwsl -d Ubuntu   \u91cd\u542f\nps -p 1 -o comm=      # \u9a8c\u8bc1 systemd \u662f\u5426\u751f\u6548\uff0c\u8f93\u51fa systemd \u5373\u6210\u529f\n```\n\n2. \u5982\u679c\u5df2\u7ecf\u5b89\u88c5\u4e86docker\uff0c\u53ef\u4ee5\u5148\u5378\u8f7d\n```\nsudo apt-get remove docker docker-engine docker.io containerd runc\n```\n\n3. \u66f4\u65b0\u7d22\u5f15\u5e76\u5b89\u88c5\u4f9d\u8d56\n```\nsudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade -y\nsudo apt-get install ca-certificates curl gnupg\n```\n\n4. \u6dfb\u52a0 Docker \u5b98\u65b9 GPG \u5bc6\u94a5\uff08\u4f7f\u7528\u963f\u91cc\u4e91\u955c\u50cf\uff09\n```\nsudo install -m 0755 -d /etc/apt/keyrings\ncurl -fsSL https://mirrors.aliyun.com/docker-ce/linux/ubuntu/gpg | sudo gpg --dearmor -o /etc/apt/keyrings/docker.gpg\nsudo chmod a+r /etc/apt/keyrings/docker.gpg\n```\n\n5. \u6dfb\u52a0 Docker \u8f6f\u4ef6\u6e90\n```\necho 'deb [arch=$(dpkg --print-architecture) signed-by=/etc/apt/keyrings/docker.gpg] https://mirrors.aliyun.com/docker-ce/linux/ubuntu $(. /etc/os-release && echo '$VERSION_CODENAME') stable' | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/docker.list > /dev/null\n```\n\n6. \u5b89\u88c5 Docker\n```\nsudo apt-get update\nsudo apt-get install docker-ce docker-ce-cli containerd.io docker-buildx-plugin docker-compose-plugin\n```\n\n7. \u914d\u7f6e Docker \u955c\u50cf\u52a0\u901f\u5668\n\u5efa\u8bae\u914d\u7f6e\u591a\u4e2a\u5907\u7528\u5730\u5740\u6216\u4f7f\u7528\u4e2a\u4eba\u7684\u963f\u91cc\u4e91\u52a0\u901f\u5668\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1776246642, "style": "", "script": "<script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/backtop.js'></script><script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/articletoc.js'></script><script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/lightbox.js'></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://github.com/junwindxqw.png", "createdDate": "2026-04-15", "dateLabelColor": "#1f883d"}, "P34": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/docker-an-zhuang-memos.html", "labels": ["docker"], "postTitle": "docker\u5b89\u88c5memos", "postUrl": "post/docker-an-zhuang-memos.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/junwindxqw/junwindxqw.github.io/issues/34", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 3038, "description": "## \u4e00\u952e\u641e\u5b9a\u7248\n```sh\n docker run -d \\        \u540e\u53f0\u8fd0\u884c \n  --name memos \\      \u5bb9\u5668\u7684\u540d\u79f0\n  --restart unless-stopped \\      \u5f00\u673a / \u5d29\u6e83\u81ea\u52a8\u91cd\u542f\n  -p 5230:5230 \\       \u4e3b\u673a5230\u7aef\u53e3 \uff1a\u6620\u5c04\u5230\u5bb9\u5668\u4e2d5230\u7aef\u53e3\n  -v ~/.memos/:/var/opt/memos \\         \u6570\u636e\u6301\u4e45\u5316 \u4e3b\u673a~/.memos\u76ee\u5f55 \uff1a \u6620\u5c04\u5230\u5bb9\u5668/var/opt/memos\n  neosmemo/memos:stable         \u955c\u50cf\u540d\u79f0\n```\n\n## Docker Compose \u7248\n```sh\n# \u521b\u5efa\u76ee\u5f55\nmkdir -p ~/docker/memos && cd ~/docker/memos\n\n# \u65b0\u5efa docker-compose.yml\nvim docker-compose.yml\n```\n\ndocker-compose.yml \u6587\u4ef6\u4e2d\u7684\u5185\u5bb9\uff1a\n```yaml \nversion: '3.8'  # \u65b0\u7248\u672c\u8fd9\u4e2a\u5b57\u6bb5\u5df2\u5e9f\u5f03\uff0c\u53ef\u4ee5\u4e0d\u52a0\u4e86\n\nservices:\n  memos:    # memos\u670d\u52a1\n    image: neosmemo/memos:stable  # \u955c\u50cf\n    container_name: memos  # \u5bb9\u5668\u540d\u79f0\n    restart: unless-stopped    # \u6302\u6389\u4e86\u81ea\u52a8\u91cd\u542f\n    ports:    # \u7aef\u53e3\u6620\u5c04\n      - '5230:5230'    # \u672c\u673a\u7aef\u53e3\uff1a\u5bb9\u5668\u7aef\u53e3\n    volumes:   # \u6570\u636e\u5377\n      - ./data:/var/opt/memos   # \u6570\u636e\u6301\u4e45\u5316\u5230\u5f53\u524d\u76ee\u5f55 ./data       \u672c\u673a\u76ee\u5f55\uff1a\u5bb9\u5668\u76ee\u5f55\n    environment:    # \u73af\u5883\u53d8\u91cf\n      - TZ=Asia/Shanghai   # \u65f6\u533a\n```\n\n```\n# \u540e\u53f0\u542f\u52a8\uff08\u9996\u6b21\u81ea\u52a8\u62c9\u955c\u50cf\uff09\ndocker compose up -d\n\n# \u67e5\u770b\u8fd0\u884c\u72b6\u6001\ndocker compose ps\n\n# \u67e5\u770b\u65e5\u5fd7\uff08\u6392\u9519\uff09\ndocker compose logs -f\n```\n\n## \u8bbf\u95ee\n\u672c\u5730\uff1ahttp://localhost:5230\n\u670d\u52a1\u5668\uff1ahttp://\u670d\u52a1\u5668IP:5230\n\n\u9996\u6b21\u8bbf\u95ee\u4f1a\u8981\u6c42\u521b\u5efa\u7ba1\u7406\u5458\u8d26\u53f7\uff08\u7b2c\u4e00\u4e2a\u7528\u6237\u5c31\u662f\u7ba1\u7406\u5458\uff09\n\n\n## docker compose \u5e38\u7528\u7ba1\u7406\u547d\u4ee4\n```bash\n# \u505c\u6b62\ndocker compose stop\n\n# \u542f\u52a8\ndocker compose start\n\n# \u91cd\u542f\ndocker compose restart\n\n# \u505c\u6b62\u5e76\u5220\u9664\u5bb9\u5668\uff08\u6570\u636e\u5377 ./data \u4e0d\u4f1a\u5220\uff09\ndocker compose down\n\n# \u66f4\u65b0\u955c\u50cf\uff08\u91cd\u65b0\u62c9\u6700\u65b0 stable\uff09\ndocker compose pull && docker compose up -d\n```\n\n\n## \u6570\u636e\u5907\u4efd\u4e0e\u8fc1\u79fb\n- \u6570\u636e\u5168\u90e8\u5728\uff1a./data\uff08\u6216\u4f60\u6302\u8f7d\u7684\u672c\u5730\u76ee\u5f55\uff09\n- \u5907\u4efd\uff1a\u76f4\u63a5\u6253\u5305 ./data \u6587\u4ef6\u5939\n- \u8fc1\u79fb\uff1a\u628a ./data \u590d\u5236\u5230\u65b0\u670d\u52a1\u5668\uff0c\u7528\u540c\u6837 docker-compose.yml \u542f\u52a8\u5373\u53ef\n\n\n## \u5e38\u89c1\u95ee\u9898\n- \u7aef\u53e3\u88ab\u5360\u7528\uff1a\u6539\u7aef\u53e3\uff1a-p 5231:5230\uff08\u5bbf\u4e3b\u673a\u7aef\u53e3\u6539\u6210 5231\uff09\n- \u6743\u9650\u62a5\u9519\uff1a\u7ed9\u76ee\u5f55\u6743\u9650\uff1achmod -R 755 ./data\n- \u56fd\u5185\u62c9\u955c\u50cf\u6162\uff1a\u53ef\u4f7f\u7528\u955c\u50cf\uff1adocker.xuanyuan.run/neosmemo/memos:stable\n\n## \u5173\u4e8erestart: unless-stopped\u914d\u7f6e\u9879\n\n<img width='549' height='459' alt='Image' src='https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/6f5b8944-3a0b-4d2b-b7aa-c79b4ba3ffa5' />\n\n## docker compose up -d \u548c docker compose start \u533a\u522b\uff1f\n\ndocker compose start\uff1a\u53ea\u542f\u52a8\u5df2\u5b58\u5728\u7684\u5bb9\u5668\uff08\u4e0d\u91cd\u5efa\u3001\u4e0d\u66f4\u65b0\u3001\u4e0d\u8bfb\u65b0\u914d\u7f6e\uff09\n\ndocker compose up -d\uff1a\u521b\u5efa / \u91cd\u5efa / \u66f4\u65b0\u5bb9\u5668 + \u542f\u52a8\uff08\u4f1a\u8bfb\u6700\u65b0\u914d\u7f6e\uff09\n\n<img width='319' height='435' alt='Image' src='https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a10b3dba-0c19-40fa-abb8-8a0e12dafaa2' />\n\n<img width='444' height='556' alt='Image' src='https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/ac2bbc5c-430c-41fe-8feb-5a57b3cc03d7' />\n\n\u65e5\u5e38\u91cd\u542f\uff08\u4e0d\u6539\u914d\u7f6e\uff09docker compose restart\n\n\u6539\u4e86\u914d\u7f6e\u6587\u4ef6\uff08\u6bd4\u5982\u7aef\u53e3\u3001\u76ee\u5f55\uff09docker compose up -d\n\n\u66f4\u65b0 Memos \u6700\u65b0\u7248    docker compose pull;    docker compose up -d\n\nstart = \u53ea\u542f\u52a8\u65e7\u5bb9\u5668\nup -d = \u6309\u6700\u65b0\u914d\u7f6e\u91cd\u65b0\u521b\u5efa\u5e76\u542f\u52a8\n\n\u6ce8\u610f\uff1a\ndocker compose up -d \u4e0d\u4f1a\u81ea\u52a8\u4e0b\u8f7d\u65b0\u7248\u955c\u50cf\uff01\n\u5b83\u53ea\u4f1a\u7528\u3010\u672c\u5730\u5df2\u7ecf\u6709\u7684\u955c\u50cf\u3011\u6765\u542f\u52a8\u5bb9\u5668\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1776310758, "style": "", "script": "<script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/backtop.js'></script><script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/articletoc.js'></script><script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/lightbox.js'></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://github.com/junwindxqw.png", "createdDate": "2026-04-16", "dateLabelColor": "#1f883d"}, "P35": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/WSL -yu- Win -wen-jian-hu-fang.html", "labels": ["wsl"], "postTitle": "WSL \u4e0e Win \u6587\u4ef6\u4e92\u8bbf", "postUrl": "post/WSL%20-yu-%20Win%20-wen-jian-hu-fang.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/junwindxqw/junwindxqw.github.io/issues/35", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 109, "description": "win \u7684\u78c1\u76d8\u6302\u8f7d\u5728 wsl \u7684 /mnt \u4e0b\n```\n/mnt/c/\n/mnt/d/\n```\nwsl \u5728 win \u7684\u8bbf\u95ee\u8def\u5f84\n```\n\\\\wsl.localhost\n\\\\wsl$\nexplorer.exe .\n```\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1776581615, "style": "", "script": "<script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/backtop.js'></script><script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/articletoc.js'></script><script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/lightbox.js'></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://github.com/junwindxqw.png", "createdDate": "2026-04-19", "dateLabelColor": "#1f883d"}, "P36": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/ubuntu-an-zhuang-nginx.html", "labels": ["Ubuntu", "Nginx"], "postTitle": "ubuntu\u5b89\u88c5nginx", "postUrl": "post/ubuntu-an-zhuang-nginx.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/junwindxqw/junwindxqw.github.io/issues/36", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 658, "description": "## \u5b89\u88c5\n```\nsudo apt update\nsudo apt install nginx -y\nnginx -v    # \u67e5\u770b\u662f\u5426\u5df2\u5b89\u88c5\nsudo systemctl status nginx   # \u67e5\u770b\u662f\u5426\u5728\u8fd0\u884c\n```\n\u6d4f\u89c8\u5668\u8bbf\u95ee\uff1ahttp://localhost/\n\n## \u5e38\u7528\u7ba1\u7406\u547d\u4ee4\n```\n# \u542f\u52a8 Nginx\nsudo systemctl start nginx\n\n# \u505c\u6b62 Nginx\nsudo systemctl stop nginx\n\n# \u91cd\u542f Nginx\uff08\u4fee\u6539\u914d\u7f6e\u540e\u5fc5\u7528\uff09\nsudo systemctl restart nginx\n\n# \u91cd\u65b0\u52a0\u8f7d\u914d\u7f6e\uff08\u4e0d\u4e2d\u65ad\u670d\u52a1\uff0c\u63a8\u8350\uff09\nsudo systemctl reload nginx\n\n# \u8bbe\u7f6e\u5f00\u673a\u81ea\u542f\nsudo systemctl enable nginx\n\n# \u53d6\u6d88\u5f00\u673a\u81ea\u542f\nsudo systemctl disable nginx\n```\n\n## Nginx \u6838\u5fc3\u6587\u4ef6\u8def\u5f84\n- \u4e3b\u914d\u7f6e\u6587\u4ef6\uff1a/etc/nginx/nginx.conf\n    - \u7f51\u7ad9\u914d\u7f6e\u76ee\u5f55\uff1a/etc/nginx/sites-available/\n    - \u542f\u7528\u7684\u7f51\u7ad9\u914d\u7f6e\uff1a/etc/nginx/sites-enabled/\n    - \u9ed8\u8ba4\u7f51\u9875\u6839\u76ee\u5f55\uff1a/var/www/html/\n- \u65e5\u5fd7\u76ee\u5f55\uff1a\n     - \u8bbf\u95ee\u65e5\u5fd7\uff1a/var/log/nginx/access.log\n    - \u9519\u8bef\u65e5\u5fd7\uff1a/var/log/nginx/error.log\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1776588440, "style": "", "script": "<script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/backtop.js'></script><script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/articletoc.js'></script><script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/lightbox.js'></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://github.com/junwindxqw.png", "createdDate": "2026-04-19", "dateLabelColor": "#1f883d"}, "P37": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/composer dump-autoload.html", "labels": ["PHP", "composer"], "postTitle": "composer dump-autoload", "postUrl": "post/composer%20dump-autoload.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/junwindxqw/junwindxqw.github.io/issues/37", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 188, "description": "\u9996\u6b21\u90e8\u7f72\uff0c\u6267\u884c composer update \u4f1a\u5b89\u88c5\u66f4\u65b0\u4f9d\u8d56\uff0c\u5e76\u4e14\u751f\u6210\u4e00\u4e2a composer.lock\uff0c\u8fd9\u4e2a\u6587\u4ef6\u662f\u7528\u6765\u9501\u5b9a\u4f9d\u8d56\u7248\u672c\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1776678559, "style": "", "script": "<script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/backtop.js'></script><script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/articletoc.js'></script><script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/lightbox.js'></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://github.com/junwindxqw.png", "createdDate": "2026-04-20", "dateLabelColor": "#1f883d"}, "P38": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/phpstorm-da-liang-bian-geng-wen-jian.html", "labels": ["phpstorm", "wsl", "Git"], "postTitle": "phpstorm\u5927\u91cf\u53d8\u66f4\u6587\u4ef6", "postUrl": "post/phpstorm-da-liang-bian-geng-wen-jian.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/junwindxqw/junwindxqw.github.io/issues/38", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 511, "description": "## CRLF/LF\nFile \u2192 Settings \u2192 Editor \u2192 Code Style \u2192 Line separator  \uff1a  Unix and macOS (\\n) \nFile Encodings  \u2192 Default line separator  \uff1a LF\n\n\u914d\u7f6e Git \u5ffd\u7565\u884c\u5c3e\u8f6c\u6362\uff0c\u5728 WSL \u7ec8\u7aef\u91cc\u6267\u884c\n\n    # \u5173\u95ed\u81ea\u52a8\u8f6c\u6362\u884c\u5c3e\n    git config --global core.autocrlf false\n\n    # \u5f3a\u5236\u4f7f\u7528 LF\n    git config --global core.eol lf\n\n    # \u5ffd\u7565\u6587\u4ef6\u6743\u9650\u53d8\u5316\uff08\u7b2c\u4e8c\u4e2a\u5e38\u89c1\u539f\u56e0\uff09\n    git config --global core.filemode false\n\n    # \u5f3a\u5236\u91cd\u7f6e\u5de5\u4f5c\u533a\u72b6\u6001\n    git checkout .    // git restore . \n\n## PhpStorm \u7528\u4e86 Windows \u7684 Git\nFile \u2192 Settings \u2192 Version Control \u2192 Git  \uff1a`\\\\wsl.localhost\\Ubuntu\\user\\bin\\git`\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1776736864, "style": "", "script": "<script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/backtop.js'></script><script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/articletoc.js'></script><script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/lightbox.js'></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://github.com/junwindxqw.png", "createdDate": "2026-04-21", "dateLabelColor": "#1f883d"}, "P39": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/ubuntu-pu-tong-yong-hu-mian-mi-ma.html", "labels": ["wsl"], "postTitle": "ubuntu\u666e\u901a\u7528\u6237\u514d\u5bc6\u7801", "postUrl": "post/ubuntu-pu-tong-yong-hu-mian-mi-ma.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/junwindxqw/junwindxqw.github.io/issues/39", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 209, "description": "```\nsudo -i   // \u5207\u6362\u5230root\u7528\u6237\n\nvisudo -f /etc/sudoers.d/xqw\n    xqw ALL=(ALL) NOPASSWD: ALL    // \u586b\u5165\n\nnano\u4fdd\u5b58\u9000\u51fa \uff1a ctrl + o  -> \u56de\u8f66 -> ctrl + x\n\nchmod 440 /etc/sudoers.d/xqw\nsu - xqw\nsudo whoami \nsudo apt update\n```\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1776738432, "style": "", "script": "<script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/backtop.js'></script><script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/articletoc.js'></script><script src='https://junwindxqw.github.io/assets/lightbox.js'></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://github.com/junwindxqw.png", "createdDate": "2026-04-21", "dateLabelColor": "#1f883d"}, "P40": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/ubuntu-an-zhuang-claude code.html", "labels": ["claude code", "wsl"], "postTitle": "ubuntu\u5b89\u88c5claude code", "postUrl": "post/ubuntu-an-zhuang-claude%20code.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/junwindxqw/junwindxqw.github.io/issues/40", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 332, "description": "\n    sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade -y\n    \n    sudo apt install -y curl git build-essential\n    \n    curl -fsSL https://claude.ai/install.sh | bash    // \u5b89\u88c5\u4f4d\u7f6e\uff1a~/.lo